&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Why Mozilla?&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;Mozilla Corporation is the non-profit-backed technology company that has shaped the internet for the better over the last 25 years. We make pioneering brands like Firefox, the privacy-minded web browser. Now, with more than 225 million people around the world using our products each month, we’re shaping the next 25 years of technology and helping to reclaim an internet built for people, not companies. Our work focuses on diverse areas including AI, social media, security and more. And we’re doing this while never losing our focus on our core mission – to make the internet better for people.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;The Mozilla Corporation is wholly owned by the non-profit 501(c) Mozilla Foundation. This means we aren’t beholden to any shareholders — only to our mission. Along with thousands of volunteer contributors and collaborators all over the world, Mozillians design, build and distribute open-source software that enables people to enjoy the internet on their terms.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;The Opportunity&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;We’re looking for an Integrated&lt;/span&gt;&lt;strong&gt; Marketing Consultant for France &lt;/strong&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;to build and lead our 2026 French brand campaign. You’ll operate at the intersection of global strategy and local execution—bringing deep French insight into a globally coordinated marketing organization.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;Europe is at the center of a once-in-a-decade shift in how browsers compete. This role is driving a major brand campaign in 2026 to drive relevance and growth—and helping millions of people choose a better internet. You’ll drive Mozilla’s cultural relevance in France for this campaign by identifying and activating opportunities beyond the tech category, embedding the brand in moments, communities, and conversations that keep the brand top-of-mind and meaningfully considered.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;This is a critical marketing role focused:&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;Re-establishing Firefox as a relevant, differentiated brand&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;Driving user and market share growth in France&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;Leading a major campaign and activation in France&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Key Responsibilities&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;You’ll be developing and leading a specific French marketing/brand strategy and campaign in 2026. This is a temporary 6-month role focused on 2026 campaign development. You’ll partner with the Director European Integrated Marketing to shape and deliver integrated marketing campaign strategy for France, aligned to audience insights, brand priorities, product initiatives, and cultural moments.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Planning &amp;amp; Strategy&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;Develop strong thought leadership and understanding of the regional landscape in France, including consumer needs, competitive specs, and emerging macro + cultural trends&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;Collaborate cross-functionally with product marketing, media, communications/ policy teams, creative, PR, and agency partners to develop impactful campaign platforms and programs for France.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;Translate global campaign strategy into locally relevant marketing 2026 initiatives that resonate with regional audiences in France and business priorities.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Campaign Development, Collaboration &amp;amp; Execution&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;Deliver integrated 2026 French brand campaign across owned + earned + paid channels, including partnerships, brand moments, and always-on activity.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;Ensure all creative output aligns with brand standards, tone of voice, and regional market nuances.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;Strong program manager; accountable for the end-to-end execution. You will maintain clear project visibility, timelines, and stakeholder updates across this campaign.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Insights and Performance Measurements&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;Bring a measurement mindset; partnering with cross-functional teams to build measurement plans ensuring work-streams deliver quantifiable outcomes.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;Partner with analytics, insights, and media teams to track + optimize campaign performance and measure impact against business objectives.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;Own campaign and marketing performance tracking and reports to be shared with senior leaders.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Professional Profile&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;You are an inspiring, cross-functional marketer directly responsible for French marketing activity. &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;You are passionate about building data-driven marketing plans and succeed in highly collaborative environments.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;8+ years of deep consumer marketing, brand marketing, and/or strategy experience&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;Fluency/proficiency in French and English&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;Strong portfolio of product launches and growth initiatives across tech, sports, and music, with expertise in creating integrated marketing and go-to-market strategies that drive brand and commercial impact&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;Solid understanding of coordinated (owned + paid + earned) channel mix approaches that drive user acquisition, consideration, product usage, and advocacy&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;Strong grasp of quantitative test designs&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;Strives to balance both creative excellence with high quantitative performance&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;Outstanding organization and project management skills&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;Excellent collaboration skills; proven track record leading through influence&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;A self-starter with a bias for action&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;Ability to lead multiple projects concurrently and thrive in a fast-paced environment across different time zones and cultures&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;About Mozilla&amp;nbsp;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;When you work at Mozilla, you give yourself a chance to make a difference in the lives of web users everywhere. And you give us a chance to make a difference in your life every single day. Join us to work on the web as the platform and help create more opportunity and innovation for everyone online.&amp;nbsp; We’re not a normal tech company. The things we create prioritize people and their privacy over profits. We exist to make the internet a healthier,&amp;nbsp; happier place for everyone&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Commitment To Diversity, Equity and Inclusion&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;Mozilla believes in the value of diverse creative practices and forms of knowledge, and knows diversity, equity and inclusion are crucial to and enrich the company’s core mission. We encourage applications from everyone, including members of all equity-seeking communities, such as (but not limited to) women, racialized and Indigenous persons, persons with disabilities, persons of all sexual orientations, gender identities and expressions.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;We will ensure that qualified individuals with disabilities are provided reasonable accommodations to participate in the job application or interview process, to perform essential job functions, and to receive other benefits and privileges of employment, as appropriate. Please contact us at hiringaccommodation@mozilla.com to request accommodation.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;We are an equal opportunity employer. We do not discriminate on the basis of race (including hairstyle and texture), religion (including religious grooming and dress practices), gender, gender identity, gender expression, color, national origin, pregnancy, ancestry, domestic partner status, disability, sexual orientation, age, genetic predisposition, medical condition, marital status, citizenship status, military or veteran status, or any other basis covered by applicable laws. Mozilla will not tolerate discrimination or harassment based on any of these characteristics or any other unlawful behavior, conduct, or purpose.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
